# HSM collector last-value sensor conformance.
# Last-value sensors remember AddValue calls and flush the current value on Stop.

last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|create_collector
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|create_last_int_sensor|contract/last/int/latest|0
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|start
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|add_int|0|1|Ok|first
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|add_int|0|2|Warning|latest
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_sent_count|0
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|stop
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_sent_count|1
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_payload_contains|0|"Type":1
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":2
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_payload_contains|0|"Status":2
last_int_flushes_latest_on_stop|expect_payload_contains|0|"Comment":"latest"

